</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvortextwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>VortexTwin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/24/01 6:37:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: BW or CS at 49?</span><hr size=1> Happ greens out at 48. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhanabal82.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hanabal82</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/24/01 6:38:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: BW or CS at 49?</span><hr size=1> lil test <p><html><center><img src="http://members.aol.com/zerdamas/signature.ipg"></center></html> <font size="4" color="red"><i>
