Thurmadur 47 Warrior</i><font size="3" color="red">
<BR>Heaven & Earth
<BR>Saryrn</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nyargle>Nyargle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/30/01 10:23:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: BW or CS at 49?</span><hr size=1> What???  no faction hits on Wyverns????<br>
And here I was scrounging for places to kite, because I didn't want to lose faction standing with Claws of Veeshan.<br>
<br>
